node.text:
Is there anything cuter than a sea otter massaging its own face? The next time you feel lazy about taking care of your skin, think of this sea otter. Wild otters clean, scrub, and exfoliate their skin daily, and do so more vigorously after a meal to rid their fur of any leftover juices.

Video by @lawrencesmith27
